<main>

  <section style="padding-top:64px;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our mission</p>
      <h1>Put a book, and a byline, within reach of every student in RYK.</h1>
      <p class="lede">We exist to close two gaps at once: the distance between a household and its nearest book, and the distance between a student writer and their first real reader.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our four pillars</p>
      <h2>What we're actually trying to do.</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
        <div class="card raised">
          <p class="callnumber">PILLAR 01</p>
          <h3 style="margin-top:10px;">Access before everything</h3>
          <p>No membership card, no fee, no waiting list. If a book lane is nearby, anyone should be able to walk up and take a book the same day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card raised">
          <p class="callnumber">PILLAR 02</p>
          <h3 style="margin-top:10px;">A real audience for student writers</h3>
          <p>Every essay and story we publish is read by people outside the writer's own classroom — neighbours, other students, and visitors to this site.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card raised">
          <p class="callnumber">PILLAR 03</p>
          <h3 style="margin-top:10px;">Reading in the languages we speak</h3>
          <p>Urdu, Saraiki and English all sit on the same shelf. We don't treat local languages as a lesser section of the lane.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card raised">
          <p class="callnumber">PILLAR 04</p>
          <h3 style="margin-top:10px;">Built and maintained locally</h3>
          <p>Every lane has a nearby shopkeeper, family or student group that looks after it. Nothing here is meant to run from far away.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Where we're headed</p>
        <h2>The next stretch of lane.</h2>
        <p class="lede">These are the goals we're currently raising funds and volunteer hours toward.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid" style="gap:16px;">
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;align-items:center;">
          <div><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 4px;">10 new book lanes</h3><p style="margin:0;color:var(--ink-70);font-size:.95rem;">across neighbourhoods that currently have none</p></div>
          <span class="callnumber">GOAL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;align-items:center;">
          <div><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 4px;">A printed annual anthology</h3><p style="margin:0;color:var(--ink-70);font-size:.95rem;">collecting the year's best student essays</p></div>
          <span class="callnumber">GOAL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;align-items:center;">
          <div><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 4px;">Weekend reading circles in 5 more schools</h3><p style="margin:0;color:var(--ink-70);font-size:.95rem;">led by trained student volunteers</p></div>
          <span class="callnumber">GOAL</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-ink">
    <div class="wrap" style="text-align:center;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Help us get there</p>
      <h2>None of this runs on good intentions alone.</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;margin-top:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
